                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>20 May 1854</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philada.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Sir:Your favor of <date>18th</date><lb/> is at hand. Enclosed please\n                find our<add>?</add><lb/> check on Bank of America #594 for Eighty six<lb/> 93/100.\n                of which $19.93 is for a/c <persName>A. Myerston Esq</persName><lb/> 18.00 for the\n                books just recd.<lb/> 87.93<lb/>\n                <persName>Len<add>?</add></persName> 1.00 paid in the box sent to<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Lindo</persName> (being freight from <placeName>Phila.</placeName>).\n                $84.93<lb/> we having no a/c with him <persName>Mr Moses Wolff</persName> owes in\n                our<lb/> office a day or two time. We cannot say<lb/> just where he is at this\n                moment. A letter<lb/> to our care would soon reach him<lb/> we think.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">Respy. Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(12)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Dovale &amp; Co</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(12)\">\n                <persName>L L <add>?</add></persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3js9ht84/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
